aboutBot:
Discord WikiBot is a simple, yet effective tool that grabs articles from the Discord Wiki. It's like a nice little wingman that can grab different books for you at the library!

» Want to join us, or just need a hand with getting started using the bot? [Click here.](https://discordapp.com/invite/ZRJ9Ghh)
» Want to just get started on your own? Try `?articles <article-name>` or `?articles` for the list of articles!

» Use `?servers` for a list of resource servers you can join.

» Use `?commands` to see a full list of the commands!

Can't find what you're looking for? Try tweeting [@discordapp](https://twitter.com/discordapp) or emailing [support@discordapp.com](https://support.discordapp.com/hc/en-us/requests/new)!

*Developed by OGNovuh#0003*
